@startuml svc-guest-profiles--post-guests

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #059669
    ParticipantBorderColor #374151
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #F9FAFB
    LifeLineBorderColor #6B7280
    BoxBorderColor #94A3B8
    BoxBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
    NoteBorderColor #64748B
    NoteBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
}

header [[/microservices/svc-guest-profiles/#integration-context ⬆ svc-guest-profiles Integration Context]]

title POST /guests\nRegister a new guest

participant "Client" as Client [[/applications/]]
participant "API Gateway" as GW [[/actors/#api-gateway]] #E0F2FE
participant "svc-guest-profiles" as Svc [[/microservices/svc-guest-profiles/]] #EDE9FE
participant "IDVerify API" as ExtID [[/actors/#idverify-api]] #F3F4F6
queue "Kafka" as Kafka [[/actors/#event-bus]] #F5F3FF
database "PostgreSQL" as DB [[/microservices/svc-guest-profiles/#data-store]] #FEF9C3

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-guest-profiles.html#/Guests/createGuest View in Swagger UI]]
end note

Client -> GW : POST /guests
activate GW #059669
GW -> Svc : route request
activate Svc #059669

note right of Svc : Validate request body

== Cross-Service Integration ==

Svc -> ExtID : Verify identity document
activate ExtID #F3F4F6
ExtID --> Svc : OK
deactivate ExtID

== Database ==

Svc -> DB : INSERT INTO ...
activate DB #FEF9C3
DB --> Svc : Created row
deactivate DB

== Async Events ==

Svc ->> Kafka : [[/events/#guestregistered guest.registered]]

Svc --> GW : 201 Created
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 201 Created
deactivate GW

@enduml